snippet.title: Amber heard replaces aquaman in the next justice league movie
snippet.description:
#justiceforjhonny #justiceleague #DCcomics

In an interestingly bad move on the part of WB they decided to increase the screen time of amber heard. They decided to replace aqua man with Mera in the up and coming justice league movie. They did this in the sake of diversity using one of the most controversial actresses there is.
